fix: cascade color system, goals page, universal format utilities

Color Architecture (Critical Fix):
- Restore :root = light mode, [data-theme=dark] = dark mode
  (industry-standard pattern matching layout.tsx theme init script)
- Previous session reversed this causing light mode to be broken
- Card and KPI card backgrounds now use var(--bg-card) token
- Segmented control dark mode now uses var(--bg-hover) and var(--border)

GoalsClient:
- Remove all hardcoded hex colors throughout
- goalStyle() now uses CSS token vars exclusively
- Hero banner gradient uses HSL tokens instead of hardcoded hex
- AddFundsModal previews new total and progress percentage live

Format Utility (src/lib/format.ts - new file):
- fmtFull, fmtPrecise, fmtCompact, fmtAdaptive, fmtWithSub, fmtPct
- Adaptive mode auto-switches at 999K threshold
- Prevents large number overflow in all display contexts

Large Number Display:
- Responsive font-size: scales down at 1M and 10M breakpoints
- text-overflow ellipsis as safety guard on all amount containers
- Dashboard, Goals, Loans all updated to use fmtAdaptive
- Hero stat colors updated to use var() tokens
